{{Infobox Berry |name = Durin |image = [[File:Durin.png]] |caption = This Berry is tremendously bitter. Just one bite is enough to instantly stop hiccups. |growtime = 6h 0m 0s |harvest = 33 berries |replant = 10% |points = 1,050 |flavor = {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 30 {{!}} 10 }} '''Durin''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding a [[Rabuta]] berry with at least 130, but no more than 160 points of bitter and no more than 80 points of all other flavours. The [[Rabuta]] berry will then have a chance to mutate into this berry.
